                        tímasett til <origDate notBefore="1400" notAfter="1450"
                           >c1400-1450</origDate> og bl. <locus from="2r"
                           facs="#AM02-0238-XIX-0002r" to="2r">2</locus> til <origDate
                           notBefore="1450" notAfter="1500">c1450-1500</origDate> (sjá <bibl>
                           <ref xml:id="ONPregistre" target="ONPregistre">ONPRegistre</ref></bibl>,
                        bls. 437). Í <bibl>
                           <ref target="KKKat">Katalog I</ref></bibl>, bls. <ref
                           target="https://baekur.is/bok/c9ff2011-3cda-4197-90ef-7e14fc19f264/1/218"
                           >203</ref>, eru blöðin tímasett í einu lagi til 15. aldar.</p>
                  </origin>
